  <main>
    <section identifier="/ca-mountain-view/part-i/article-v/section-509"
             temporalId="sSection 509">
      <num>Section 509</num>
      <heading>Quorum</heading>
      <content>
        <p>A majority of the council shall constitute a quorum for the transaction of business,
               but a less number may adjourn from time to time and postpone the consideration of
               pending business.</p>
      </content>
    </section>
  </main>
